---
title: Creamy Leek & Veggie Risoni with Herby Roasted Kumara & Parmesan
description: What’s going into the risoni today? A little bit of leek, a heap of roasted kumara, a touch of capsicum also roasted to add that delicious
hint of smokiness and finally a sprinkling of herby seasoning. It’s a perfect concoction of flavour, texture and pure yumminess.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-leek-veggie-risoni-40709a53.jpg
